  "summaryViHtml": "<h2>Tóm tắt</h2><p>Thẻ Hàng Hải là một danh mục chế tạo dành riêng cho các DLC Shipwrecked và Hamlet.</p>",
  "title": "Nautical Tab",
  "wikitext": "{{Exclusivity|Shipwrecked|Hamlet}}\n{{Quote|My pride and joy!|Walani}}[[File:Icon Nautical.png|thumb|104x104px|Nautical Icon.]]\nThe '''Nautical Tab''' is a crafting category exclusive to the ''[[Shipwrecked]]'' and ''[[Hamlet]]'' DLCs.\n\nIn ''Shipwrecked'' it contains [[Boats]], most items related to them, as well as other items and structures that are useful in surviving and farming the [[Ocean]] biome. Boats are the only way to travel between islands in the world of ''Shipwrecked''. The player will start off able to build either a [[Raft]] or [[Log Raft]] to get around, unless playing as [[Wickerbottom]], [[Walani]] or [[Woodlegs]], as they will have the [[Row Boat]], the [[Surfboard]] or the [[The 'Sea Legs']] available to craft right away, respectively.\n\nThe more advanced boats have their own equipment slots for a [[Sail]], a light source, a [[Boat Cannon]], a [[Quackering Ram]] or a [[Trawl Net]]. The [[Cargo Boat]] gives six additional inventory slots, and the [[Encrusted Boat]] has the most durability out of all available boats. This category also contains all [[Dress Tab|Dress]] [[items]] related to boats like the [[Pirate Hat]] or the [[Life Jacket]].\n\nIn ''Hamlet'' the Tab contains only some of the items available in ''Shipwrecked'': Log Rafts, Row Boats, Cargo Boats, Boat Repair Kit and Snakeskin Sails are available to craft, the latter one looking very different. Additionally, the [[Cork Bowl Canoe]] is added to this tab.\n\n== Craftable Items and Structures ==\nThe following items and structures can be crafted in the Nautical Tab:\n\n<div style=\"clear:both; font-weight: bold\"><gallery columns=\"7\" position=\"center\" widths=\"64\" captionalign=\"center\" captionsize=\"medium\" bordersize=\"none\" spacing=\"medium\" hideaddbutton=\"true\" navigation=\"true\">\nSurfboard.png|[[Surfboard]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}{{Pic|20|Walani Portrait|Walani}}|link=Surfboard\nLucky Hat.png|[[Lucky Hat]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}{{Pic|20|Woodlegs Portrait|Woodlegs}}|link=Lucky Hat\nThe 'Sea Legs'.png|[[The 'Sea Legs']]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}{{Pic|20|Woodlegs Portrait|Woodlegs}}|link=The 'Sea Legs'\nLog Raft.png|[[Log Raft]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Log Raft\nRaft.png|[[Raft]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Raft\nRow Boat.png|[[Row Boat]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Row Boat\nCargo Boat.png|[[Cargo Boat]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Cargo Boat\nArmoured Boat.png|[[Armored Boat]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Armored Boat\nEncrusted Boat.png|[[Encrusted Boat]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Encrusted Boat\nBoat Repair Kit.png|[[Boat Repair Kit]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Boat Repair Kit\nThatch Sail.png|[[Thatch Sail]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Thatch Sail\nCloth Sail.png|[[Cloth Sail]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Cloth Sail\nSnakeskin Sail.png|[[Snakeskin Sail]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Snakeskin Sail\nFeather Lite Sail.png|[[Feather Lite Sail]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Feather Lite Sail\nIron Wind.png|[[Iron Wind]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Iron Wind\nBoat Cannon.png|[[Boat Cannon]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Boat Cannon\nSea Trap.png|[[Sea Trap]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Sea Trap\nTrawl Net.png|[[Trawl Net]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Trawl Net\nSpyglass.png|[[Spyglass]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Spyglass\nSuper Spyglass.png|[[Super Spyglass]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Super Spyglass\nCaptain Hat.png|[[Captain Hat]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Captain Hat\nPirate Hat.png|[[Pirate Hat]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Pirate Hat\nLife Jacket.png|[[Life Jacket]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Life Jacket\nBuoy.png|[[Buoy]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Buoy\nQuackering Ram.png|[[Quackering Ram]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Quackering Ram\nTar Extractor.png|[[Tar Extractor]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Tar Extractor\nSea Yard.png|[[Sea Yard]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Sea Yard\nCork Bowl Canoe.png|[[Cork Bowl Canoe]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}|link=Cork Bowl Canoe\n</gallery></div>\n\n{{Tabs}}\n\n__NOTOC__\n[[Category:Crafting Tabs]]\n[[Category:Shipwrecked]]\n[[Category:Hamlet]]\n[[ko:항해 탭]]"
